OL,3,CFootage shows vehicle 'wreckage' after
OL,4,Cman drove wrong way on carriageway
OL,6,FA man who drove up the A3 in the wrong
OL,7,Fdirection, at more than double the
OL,8,Fdrink and drug drive limits, has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FOfficers were alerted to a van driving
OL,12,Fnorth on the southbound carriageway at
OL,13,FThursley just before 2.15am on Sunday
OL,14,F18 December 2022.
OL,16,FThe van was involved in a three-
OL,17,Fvehicle collision just outside
OL,18,FGuildford, causing substantial
OL,19,Fwreckage to be scattered across the
OL,20,Froad.
