OL,6,FThe people in the other vehicles were
OL,7,Fable to climb from their cars before
OL,8,Fpolice arrived and they received
OL,9,Fmedical attention at the scene.
OL,11,FThe van driver, Shane Mackay, of
OL,12,FFarnham, was found lying on the front
OL,13,Fseat of the van, conscious but
OL,14,Fsmelling of alcohol and slurring his
OL,15,Fspeech.
OL,17,FHe was cut from his vehicle and taken
OL,18,Fto hospital with minor injuries.
