OL,6,FAfter initially pleading not guilty,
OL,7,Fhe later changed this to a guilty plea
OL,8,Fand was given a 16-month custodial
OL,9,Fsentence for dangerous driving, at
OL,10,FGuildford Crown Court on Thursday, 2
OL,11,FMay.
OL,13,FHe was also sentenced to 13 weeks for
OL,14,Fdrug driving to run concurrently and
OL,15,Fdisqualified from driving for four
OL,16,Fyears (51 months).
OL,18,FAfter this disqualification period has
OL,19,Fpassed, Mackay will be required to
OL,20,Ftake an extended retest if he wishes
OL,21,Fto have a new driving licence.
