OL,6,FPS Dan Ayrton from the Surrey Roads
OL,7,FPolicing Unit said: "This case shows
OL,8,Fthe shocking reality of what can
OL,9,Fhappen if you choose to get behind the
OL,10,Fwheel while intoxicated through drink
OL,11,For drugs.
OL,13,F"When you see the wreckage of the
OL,14,Fvehicles involved it is sheer luck
OL,15,Fthat no one was killed or seriously
OL,16,Finjured in this case.
OL,18,F"Drink and drug driving will not be
OL,19,Ftolerated on Surrey's roads and you
OL,20,Fshould expect to pay the maximum
OL,21,Fpenalty if you are caught.
