OL,6,F"I am thankful to the members of the
OL,7,Fpublic who quickly called us to report
OL,8,Fthis incident and I would encourage
OL,9,Fanyone who thinks they may be
OL,10,Fwitnessing a drink or drug driver to
OL,11,Fcontact us. We will act and use the
OL,12,Ffull power of the law to remove
OL,13,Fdangerous drivers from our roads and
OL,14,Fprotect you and your loved ones."
